vertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559485297","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545731228,"updated_time":1545731228,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":299,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“那！当然可以啦！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“北大请你来当教授！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——李伟固\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":558971297,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458","url_token":"shu-xue-jian-mo-lao-si-ji","name":"数学建模老司机","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f85fdd994d7a2646c5e3aeaf3bbbbf1a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f85fdd994d7a2646c5e3aeaf3bbbbf1a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/298c7816e6ec5e00fd565672fed0b458","user_type":"people","headline":"抵制美赛，从我做起！","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/558971297","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-02d8071015a6dd12d70a5082abb230fb_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545663978,"updated_time":1546147597,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5733,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果真的有的话，那么会：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e直接授予博士学位，聘为正教授+博士生导师，推荐申请长江学者+国家杰出青年基金，享受国务院特殊津贴，颁发求是杰出科学家奖，列为中国科学院数学物理学部院士候选人，参评下一年度国家自然科学一等奖，提前预订2022年圣彼得堡国际数学家大会一小时报告+菲尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺便提个建议，最好把论文投到Annals of Mathematics上，发表在知乎有点太可惜了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76e19b5b4b5ecf6cdaf61962928ca994_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1728\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d6a01061736661a0e4cbf5dc6404893d_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76e19b5b4b5ecf6cdaf61962928ca994_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1440'%20height='1728'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1728\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d6a01061736661a0e4cbf5dc6404893d_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76e19b5b4b5ecf6cdaf61962928ca994_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76e19b5b4b5ecf6cdaf61962928ca994_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e镜像问题：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307397954/answer/562491739\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果高中生研发出埃博拉病毒疫苗，会被清华北大生命科学学院保送吗？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307030887/answer/562795672\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-eb8b6fea351c49a5f1aaf3dec74a3aec_bh.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1280\" data-image-height=\"2276\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如何看待高中生声称证明哥德巴赫猜想？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562535130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b7495a21eea6c4353196a4d90a5d2aa2","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562535130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546097760,"updated_time":1546097760,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":31,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主你还是太弱了，我小学四年级的时候由一道竞赛题引申出发“证明”了哥猜... 虽然回家仔细思考发现只证明了一部分经过特殊构造的数满足条件（具体怎样我忘了，我的竞赛水平自那以后再也没增长过，现在也挺后悔的）。中二时期谁都有过，而你能获得的不是知乎骗来的粉丝，保送北大清华出人头地...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而是那份数学带给你的纯粹的快乐，倾心解题的专注，完成书本知识后自由思考的自信与骄傲。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使我们变成瞟一眼数学书就去刷手机、翘微积分课打游戏的大学生，变成油腻的中年大叔，做着与数学不相干的工作，我依然记得并不后悔做那个课间颤抖着把自己的“证明”递给老师的小男孩。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e醒醒吧、不要玷污了这份纯粹，也不要放弃一些你本该能得到的教训。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563759515,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8315b5eeb7610b8d711a7949ce6155dd","url_token":"wei-long-27-11","name":"微草成原出毫末","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-963b41611dd8f8512e6e96fa38bd15d8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-963b41611dd8f8512e6e96fa38bd15d8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8315b5eeb7610b8d711a7949ce6155dd","user_type":"people","headline":"蜉蝣及夕而死，夏蝉不知春秋","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563759515","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273544,"updated_time":1546273544,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":108,"content":"\u003cp\u003e善人的包容是畜生的乐园 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我希望人们能够骂醒他打醒他而