经过系统的学习也是可以取的一些研究成果的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559515191,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1f2b8e45afd14c6515dbeb39d5dd3bc2","url_token":"zhou-heng-yi-36","name":"紫蓝星逸","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-91c47177e551dca341ad057bb4cc0541_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-91c47177e551dca341ad057bb4cc0541_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1f2b8e45afd14c6515dbeb39d5dd3bc2","user_type":"people","headline":"退乎，只点赞，不回答","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559515191","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545734501,"updated_time":1545881253,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":160,"content":"\u003cp\u003e好的好的，我们都等着呢！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月1号是吧？没问题，31号晚上我一定熬到十二点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们这种“官科”都算不上的不敢乱评价您，估计到时候您的证明我这种高中数学都不行的人也看不懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那些水平高深的数学家又不会专门上知乎看您的文章，那可怎么办才好？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我真的是为题主感到非常的焦虑，不过\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e单纯论手法，题主比大多数民科都强哦\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一般民科创造奇迹以后都是立马发到网上然后光速打脸。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个小朋友故意拖个几天，挑个黄道吉日，还弄个高中生人设，喷又不能喷的过分，还能顺便涨粉。你看，人家粉丝都500＋\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e唉:-(，是我咸吃萝卜淡操心了。题主肯定有办法引起数学大V们的关注，嗯⊙∀⊙！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到哥德巴赫猜想，西游记里充满了各种难以置信的奇思妙想，明年由我带头，中美合资的3D西游记，就要开拍了，文体两开花，希望大家多多关注！\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在有点不爽了，昨天看到那个匿名老师的回答，原来已经变得很友善了。但是，昨天11点多，题主又发了一篇文章，申明自己的证明根本没有外传过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在想知道，这个匿名的老师到底是不是真的？他的言辞为什么与题主不符合？是题主自己作，不承认证明有问题，还是这个匿名用户不存在，是某人假冒的？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然自称是题主的老师，说话还有理有据的，那按他的身份应该是题主的高中数学老师，为什么题主申明里用的是“那位老师”！我对这个称谓很感兴趣。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不是我黑暗，我现在怀疑是题主匿名回答，希望匿名用户或者题主出来解释解释？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560273018,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d625e057ba5c7fff539cd514b84f0329","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560273018","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545824653,"updated_time":1545824653,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":61,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在这个问题下为题主祝贺叫好的诸位忘了凡伟了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/59471035/answer/165656590\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1825018d44043bb90a9f094b49317a79_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2270\" data-image-height=\"1016\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如何评价凡伟提出的电荷不存在理论？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e立个flag，这题主要是能证明哥猜，我哈士奇的哈字换个部首。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559537938,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"60cd9664ef2f13d8d5ddba060ef35a8a","url_token":"ling-jian-94","name":"灵剑","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/fb3c5da43_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/fb3c5da43_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/60cd9664ef2f13d8d5ddba060ef35a8a","user_type":"people","headline":"擅长概率类问题","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559537938","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545737015,"updated_time":1545737015,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":103,"content":"\u003cp\u003e……高中就能解决这种问题的人，读大学不是浪费时间吗，图啥啊，混张文凭出来当程序员？？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559785440,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","url_token":"morgancheng","name":"程墨Morgan","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/04d3c071d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/29448cc28212a543bea56b9492f82e25","user_type":"people","headline":"互联网研发老兵，微信公众号morgansays，《深入浅出React和Redux》作者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559785440","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545779269,"updated_time":1545779269,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":507,"content":"\u003cp\u003e肯定不会，如果高中生就证明了哥德巴赫猜想，那还清什么华什么北什么大？全世界任何一所大学你随便挑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而，醒醒，不要幻想着高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在中科院的附近，有段时间（也许现在还有）总能看到一些人在路边闲逛，眼神呆滞，看到有人路过，就递上去一个小条，上面三言两语几个公式“证明”了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些人，就是被“证明哥德巴赫猜想就可以直接进高等学府”这种想法耽误的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561746835,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","url_token":"lian-ke-30","name":"假语","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","user_type":"people","headline":"十分冷淡存知己，一曲微茫度此生。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561746835","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995761,"updated_time":1546003532,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":222,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲失败了，是哗众取宠的小丑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲成功了，那就是睥睨四顾的成功人士了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你看，刚刚骂人家骂得正爽，觉得这种脑子的人这辈子都不能成功，可是一转眼，他现在就已经从一个民科升华成了一个移动的流量大v了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然他现在看起来还是个民科也或者高一新生。但是你看看别人关注数量，很多人拿赞同数量举例。其实他们根本不明白赞同和关注的区别\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看别人的回答流量，虽然不知道他本意是否是炒作。但是这19k的关注。和浑身上下自带的流量，加上知乎这个平台对于高关注用户的偏爱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且，19k的关注远远不是终点，现在热度还没有停止呢，并且知乎也在为了热度恶意的引导着流量\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人不相信我，那我便举几个例子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e比如这位叶青大v，他积攒了几年的粉丝为18k。用了几年的时间，而最开始他还仅仅只是一个不知名用户的时候，就依靠阅读流量获得了极多邀请合作，以及在答案里面植入广告的邀请。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而我们的高中生，证明大v。却坐拥19k的活跃用户关注，其中还包括不少大v。也就是他最少也足以在短期内达到叶青大v层次的水平，一些说只值几百块钱的朋友，我只能说你对于流量变现太没有概念了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题的流量更是可怕至极，如图所示。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前来说他的帐号价值已经上了六位数以上了。这是什么意思。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是人家选择最愚蠢的变现方式，把这个账号卖了。也足以变现数十万了，至于其他的各种变现方式，最简单就是成为一个大v开一个公众号。流量变现。足以让他在高中就月入五位数，如果经营得好。足以让自己年收入比得上一个小资家庭的年收入了，高考加分也无非请人代笔发表一篇简简单单的论文再背上一背。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在这个帐号那怕是拿来给我这种不怎么熟悉知乎各种潜规则的人来运用，也足以达成月入过万这种小目标，而给某些人能够产生的流量更是难以直接计算。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想想人家高一就能赚数十万，想出如此的完美炒作方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕是哗众取宠。人家也已经成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个案例足以位列知乎最近三年成功的钓鱼案例。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们对于钓鱼者的冷嘲热讽也无非是在赠送流量，为他的变现添砖加瓦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也不知道是有预谋的炒作还是天意如此。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只知道，他确实成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个成功者，还是值得我献上一点敬意的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕，靠的只是运气\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559871763,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c7495d847d3d0bdb85e2ed4184925a61","url_token":"qia-la-pu-yi","name":"卡拉普汉","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a44364b2b89a8441e20b8ba52ca239ee_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a44364b2b89a8441e20b8ba52ca239ee_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c7495d847d3d0bdb85e2ed4184925a61","user_type":"people","headline":"懒","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559871763","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f4a7de0d1a4cf49f70d6a7f434e0a544_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545790187,"updated_time":1545790193,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":152,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我上小学三年级弟弟，刚刚假设了多元宇宙（平行宇宙）的时间线分裂交叉及合并收束理论，大佬给看看，能保个中科大少年班不？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-58bf0e33df2b4f3e6facc0f4cfd7b1c1_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a0d68a7435faa48fb038f30e9d38878a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-58bf0e33df2b4f3e6facc0f4cfd7b1c1_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='960'%20height='540'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"960\" data-rawheight=\"540\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a0d68a7435faa48fb038f30e9d38878a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"960\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-58bf0e33df2b4f3e6facc0f4cfd7b1c1_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-58bf0e33df2b4f3e6facc0f4cfd7b1c1_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560461710,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560461710","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1e0cdf5e487ef87fdcb501e3dbfc89c9_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839596,"updated_time":1546068718,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":150,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e12.29更新：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e偶然在网上发现了科学出版社2011年出版的《哥德巴赫猜想》（第二版，潘承洞、潘承彪著\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e）的试读章节链接。感兴趣的可以点击\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ecsponline.com/yz/B64EDB42D69214CEEB63DA63C7A996100000.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e这个链接\u003c/a\u003e下载。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然只有引言，但恕我直言，贵乎上能完全读懂引言的人可能不超过【数据删除】个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有志于研究哥猜者可以去某宝或某东购买全书，并不算太贵。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e况且，再次恕我直言，\u003cb\u003e真正\u003c/b\u003e有能力研究哥猜的人应该都能够接触到图书馆。至少我查了敝校的图书馆，还是有几本的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1748'%20height='745'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e就是这本书\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e千万要注意\u003c/b\u003e不要买到徐迟所著的那个同名报（ji）告（tang）文学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今天哥猜能成为民科聚集地，不可谓没有上面那本报告文学的“功劳”呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e------------------12.29分割线------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在知乎上发表……您会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='924'%20height='716'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果不会的话，还有4天，学会Latex公式语法足够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学会Latex语法之后，在数学方面的顶级期刊发文章也是没问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果您说您的证明“根本用不到这些需要用公式编辑器才能打出来的玩意”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对不起\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e慢走不送\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-----------12.27更新分割线-----------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位仁兄似乎开了个叫“数学”的专栏……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e估计证明方法就会发在里面吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e居然有些期待呢（x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）如果半年后他真的能进入大学学习数学，这个专栏可能会成为一个能够交流数学（*真正的数学）的地方。如果真的有那一天，希望大家都忘记他当年年轻气盛时曾经声称证明了哥猜吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e （2）如果不然，那里想必要变成民科理论聚集地了。真是可怕。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e衷心希望最后结果（1）成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如下为陈景润论文里的一个公式。我当然完全看不懂\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但我至少没有声称自己证明了哥猜\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cnotag%5Csum_%7BD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+Q%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5C+%7D+%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cleqslant+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright+%29%5C%5C+%5Cnotag%5Cleqslant+%7B%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%5EiD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright+%29+%5C%5C%5Cnotag%5Cleqslant+%7B%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%282%5E%7Bi%2B2%7DD%2B%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpi+N%7D%7B2%5EiD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D%5Cleft+%7Ca_n%5Cright+%7C%5E2%5Cll%5Cleft+%28Q%2B%5Cfrac%7BN%7D%7BD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D%5Cleft+%7Ca_n%5Cright+%7C%5E%7B2%7D%5C%21\" alt=\"\\notag\\sum_{D\u0026lt;q\\leqslant Q}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\ } {\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\leqslant \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (\\sum_{2^iD\u0026lt;q\\leqslant 2^{i+1}D}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\right )\\\\ \\notag\\leqslant {} \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (\\frac{1}{2^iD}\\right )\\left (\\sum_{2^iD\u0026lt;q\\leqslant 2^{i+1}D}^{}\\frac{1}{\\varphi (q)}{\\sum_{{\\chi}_q}^{}}^{\\ast }{\\left | \\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N} a_n {\\chi}_{q}(n)\\right |}^{2}\\right ) \\\\\\notag\\leqslant {} \\sum_{i=0}^{h}\\left (2^{i+2}D+\\frac{\\pi N}{2^iD}\\right )\\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N}\\left |a_n\\right |^2\\ll\\left (Q+\\frac{N}{D}\\right )\\sum_{n=M+1}^{M+N}\\left |a_n\\right |^{2}\\!\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561326218,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1fc11ebab33c10f17269463c217027d2","url_token":"zhang-shu-rui-86-63","name":"录人","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b837dfa9376ea095d90980194622747f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b837dfa9376ea095d90980194622747f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1fc11ebab33c10f17269463c217027d2","user_type":"people","headline":"嬉笑怒骂，皆成404","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561326218","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545959188,"updated_time":1545959427,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":394,"content":"\u003cp\u003e数学我不太懂，我想说一个我懂一些的东西，文学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家可能知道，文学的门槛比数学低的多，但是大家可能不知道的是，现在写严肃文学的人的门槛已经低到了什么程度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在网络上的所谓的文圈中，有这样一些初中，高中的孩子，他们不屑于写简单的故事，更不屑于读它们。他们读尤利西斯，读2666，读喧哗与骚动，读百年孤独。他们什么难读什么，什么厚读什么，接着，就开始尝试创作他们口中的严肃文学，尝试各种小说手法，多半是意识流（也许是他们觉得这个名字比较酷）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么，当其他人看不懂他们的文字后，他们会做出很多解释，解释每一句中的意象，并通过这种解释来暗暗嘲讽读者。很多阅读他们作品的也是孩子，并没有很高的审美能力，面对不了解的事物，也只能违心地叫好，这却又导致了年幼作者的骄傲，自此，他们形成了一个完整的互赞严肃文学圈。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但实际上，当我看到他们的文学作品时，只能看到一堆上下不相关的句子，一堆生僻辞藻的堆砌，一堆没有情节推进的人物形象。当我询问他们是否创作过人物和情节俱全的简单故事时，他们会说，没有，并再次申辩，我这是福克纳/马尔克斯的写法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主发现了什么吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在是知识爆炸的时代，年轻人可以轻易地获取各种方面的知识，因此会由此产生我可以轻易完成一个伟大成果的错觉，但实际上，我不得不遗憾地告诉题主，现在想要在任何一个学科做出一个伟大成果，都比从前难的多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为现在的所有学科，职业，都已经发展到了一个极其艰深的程度，前人几百年乃至几千年的努力，已经把它们的路走的太远太宽，我们在他们的基础上创新，就已经难上加难，更何况是走出一条新路呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过题主也不用灰心，如果1月1日，题主证明了猜想，那么我会很高兴跟天才生活在同一个时代，如果没有证明，题主大可以把它当作一个少年时期的幻梦，这并不丢人，相比我们在学生时代打架斗殴，争当某某地区扛把子的梦想，这种梦不是更加健康，无害一些吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只是，人生苦短，要早点醒来啊。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=40\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=0\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
